{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015360/extras/desc_overview.png?t=1680376168\" /><br>Explore the continent of Cestina, fight against enemies in tactical battles, and become powerful enough to defeat a threat that keeps getting stronger with every day.<br>Time will play an important role, being the prime factor for events, quests, monsters behavior, shops opening time, and much more.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015360/extras/desc_story.png?t=1680376168\" /><br>Eleven years ago, the Dark Beast appeared from the Sky Tower, spreading its curse through the continent of Cestina until it was sealed by the four heroes.<br>Now that the beast has broken its seal, with the heroes nowhere to be found and a continent that hasn't yet recovered, it's up to Albus, adopted son of King Magnus, to defeat the Beast once and for all before it regains its full powers.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015360/extras/desc_features.png?t=1680376168\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tactical battles with grid-based-movement. <br></li><li>100 abilities to learn, allowing flexible playstyles.<br></li><li>Optional places and enemies, including super bosses.<br></li><li>In-game clock - Time will advance by walking, or doing actions like sleeping or fishing.<br></li><li>NPCs will act in response to time passage and your actions. Help them and you may change, or even save, their lives.<br></li><li>Complete quests to get rare items and weapons.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Dark Slime","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2015360/119dedd02f91bca3fc3f5e658ae7c74ce6083a04.jpg"},{"name":"Golem","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2015360/9f447f50418c89fb18c47b8494cba365a05